# C# conventions

- Namespace: JobsGeParser (endpoints: JobsGeParser.Endpoints)
- Nullable enabled — avoid null-forgiving unless justified
- New config: JobsGeParserOptions + appsettings.json + validation in Ext
- New services: singleton unless stateless/scoped need arises
- Use IHttpClientFactory named client "JobsGeClient" — no new static HttpClient fields
- Prefer extension methods on IServiceCollection / IEndpointRouteBuilder (match Ext.cs pattern)
